content: Great for those looking to start identifying seaweeds and those with more taxonomic experience! Even if you are unsure about a seaweed's character, this app will generate multiple possibilities of what your seaweed might be!
Really good app! The creator put tons of thought into it and it's always being updated. Very handy to avoid confusing algae keys and also when there's no internet access. Great for any skill level
This app carried me through my seaweeds course. Only improvement I can think of is maybe a search function so you don't have to scroll through all the seaweed names!

Does very well at helping you narrow down your search when trying to identify an algae. Also has the ability for just looking up specific species in a list form. I use this quite often, especially for accurate photos for visual identification since it is often quite difficult to find good photos of algae that is labeled properly as the correct species.
